  solution    : "Garantir que systemd-journald armazene logs de forma persistente."
  reference   : "BASELINE"
  see_also    : "BASELINE_UBUNTU20-24_DEBIAN11-13.csv"
  cmd         : "bash -c '(grep -REiq '\"'\"'^[[:space:]]*Storage[[:space:]]*=[[:space:]]*persistent\\b'\"'\"' /etc/systemd/journald.conf /etc/systemd/journald.conf.d/*.conf 2>/dev/null && echo \"PASS\" || echo \"FAIL\")'"
